title: Tessemae's Organic Classic Balsamic Dressing, 10 FZ
features: Tessemae’s Organic Balsamic Vinaigrette Salad Dressing is our perfectly balanced blend of organic balsmic vinegar and organic sunflower oil, with flavorful herbs and spices
Tessemae’s natural dressings, sauces, and marinades are chosen for their tasty, flavorful herbs and spices. Made with prime natural ingredients found in your kitchen
Tessemae’s Organic Balsamic Vinaigrette Dressing is Whole30 Certified, soy-free, gluten-free, and dairy-free, sugar free, and vegan, and very, very tasty
We are proud of our pure ingredients – no fillers (like xanthan gum, tapioca starch and gum acacia) in any of our products, only the highest quality organic oils and organic herbs and spices
Featuring Organic High Oleic Sunflower Oil sourced from carefully selected sources. Sunflower oil is rich in Essential Fatty Acids and antioxidants to promote holistic body health
description: Tall, dark and fruity – and ready to woo your taste buds. Organic Non-GMO Vegan Sugar Free Dairy Free Gluten Free Keto Friendly Our Organic Pantry Classic Balsamic is so much more than a salad dressing! We took a classic and made it our own. Try tossing with veggies before roasting, or as a marinade for pork and chicken. INGREDIENTS: *BALSAMIC VINEGAR, (*WINE VINEGAR, *CONCENTRATED GRAPE MUST). *HIGH OLEIC SUNFLOWER OIL, *COCONUT NECTAR (ORGANIC COCONUT TREE SAP NECTAR), *LEMON JUICE, *MUSTARD (*VINEGAR, WATER, *MUSTARD SEED, SEA SALT, *SPICES), SEA SALT, *ONION POWDER, *GARLIC POWDER, *BLACK PEPPER, *ROSEMARY EXTRACT *ORGANIC INGREDIENTS Always refer to bottle label for up-to-date ingredient and nutrition information.
